title: Jimmy Carr Comedian 2007
description:
Following the huge success of &#039;Jimmy Carr Live&#039; and &#039;Jimmy Carr Stand Up&#039;, the multi-award winning Jimmy Carr returns with his third live stand up DVD simply entitled &#039;Comedian&#039;.

Recorded live at London&#039;s Bloomsbury Theatre, the posh-suited gagster unleashes his rapid-fire wit upon his audience with jokes that are just too rude for TV.

This is Jimmy&#039;s best yet. The main show is over an hour and a half long.

Jimmy plays to over 200,000 fans every year around Britain. Watch this DVD and see what all the fuss is about.
